Short Description
Robots with human-like sentience. They contain a weakened form of an ⁠Archkin's Archose, meaning their whole being is powered by Soul Energy, not electricity.
They don't need food or drink to live, but do need a steady supply of metal to maintain their bodies if any damage is sustained.

